---
description: Defines the preferred folder structure for multi-platform monorepo projects.
globs: **/*
---
- Recommended monorepo folder structure:
  apps/
    web/                    # React Native Web app
      src/
        components/
        pages/
        hooks/
        store/              # Redux store
        types/
        utils/
    mobile/                 # React Native + Expo app
      src/
        components/
        screens/
        navigation/
        store/              # Redux store
        types/
        utils/
    desktop/                # Electron app
      src/
        main/               # Electron main process
        renderer/           # Electron renderer
          components/
          pages/
          store/            # Redux store
          types/
          utils/
  packages/
    shared/                 # Shared code
      src/
        components/
        hooks/
        store/              # Shared Redux store
        api/
        types/
        utils/
    ui/                     # Shared UI components
      src/
        components/
        styles/
  tools/                    # Build tools